Package edu.drexel.cs.jah473.datastructures

Various useful data structures.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultMap<K,V>
    A map that returns a user-defined default value when a given key is not present.
    KDTree<E extends KDPoint>
    Class to represent a dynamic KD tree data structure.
    Sparse2DArray<E>
    A space and time efficient way to represent a sparse 2D array of any data type.
    TallyMap<K>
    A map that tallies up counts for its keys.
    Trie
    Represents a dynamic trie data structure for maintaining a set of strings.
